"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"More than 200 people have been killed by US and Israeli attacks across Iran, says the Red Crescent. There are reports of Iranian retaliation in places like Dubai, Doha, Bahrain, and Kuwait. Iranians are talking about what is happening inside the country, even though the internet is almost completely shut down.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attacks in Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"M\u00e1s de 200 personas han muerto por ataques de Estados Unidos e Israel en Ir\u00e1n, dice la Cruz Roja. Hay reportes de que Ir\u00e1n responde en lugares como Dub\u00e1i, Doha, Bar\u00e9in y Kuwait. Los iran\u00edes hablan de lo que pasa en su pa\u00eds, aunque el internet casi no funciona.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques en Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Smoke and flames rose from Dubai's Fairmont The Palm hotel as civilian targets and US military bases across the Middle East came under fire.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fire in Dubai\",            \"translated_version\": \"Humo y llamas salieron del hotel Fairmont The Palm en Dub\u00e1i mientras atacaban objetivos civiles y bases militares de Estados Unidos en el Medio Oriente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Fuego en Dub\u00e1i\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Dozens of well-known groups faced shutdown under a new Israeli law, although the reprieve might be temporary.\",            \"english_title\": \"Groups Face Shutdown\",            \"translated_version\": \"Docenas de grupos conocidos podr\u00edan cerrar por una nueva ley de Israel, aunque esto podr\u00eda ser temporal.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Grupos podr\u00edan cerrar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The crowded tram was travelling in the centre of Milan at rush hour when it appeared to crash into the side of a building.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tram Crash in Milan\",            \"translated_version\": \"El tranv\u00eda lleno de gente viajaba en el centro de Mil\u00e1n en hora pico cuando choc\u00f3 contra un edificio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Choque de tranv\u00eda en Mil\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The latest attacks by Pakistan follow months of clashes between the two countries, despite agreeing to a fragile ceasefire in October.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pakistan Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los \u00faltimos ataques de Pakist\u00e1n siguen meses de peleas entre los dos pa\u00edses, aunque acordaron un alto al fuego fr\u00e1gil en octubre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques de Pakist\u00e1n\"        }    ]}"